des:
Get information about Los Angeles International Airport Flights. 

Enable the skill and say "Alexa, start L.A.X. flights" to begin. 

Get information on Flight Status:
You can find your flight information by saying the Airline Name and Flight Number (only numbers)
"Alexa, ask l. a. x. flights what is the status of Delta airlines three five four nine"
"Alexa, ask l. a. x. flights to talk about American airlines six zero two seven"
